    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Those affected by this spell work together in harmony. Any time either does something that anyone else affected by the same spell has done in the same round, they receive a +1 status bonus to the action. If two members affected by the same casting of this spell are flanking a target, increase the flanking bonus to +3.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> You may affect another willing creature within range.</p>"
